## 🏗️ Architecture & Directory Structure

# 1. Business Goals
- Create a comprehensive markdown-based knowledge base covering all known useful coding patterns, paradigms, and best practices
- Provide systematic documentation explaining why, when, and tradeoffs for each pattern
- Enable progressive learning from basic concepts to advanced patterns
- Support cross-referencing between related paradigms and anti-patterns
- Establish a reusable reference for system engineering, architecture, safety, and testing patterns

